msg.msgText: NOTES: 1. Enclose each key=value pair within double quotation marks. 2. Destination, UserID and Password are required items. 3. If Destination is set to an FTP server, the test attempts to list the files in the specified directory on the server. If "list" permission is not set on the server, the test fails.
